COMMENT ON COLUMN dbo.k12_school.charter_school_contract_approval_date IS 'The effective date of the contract (or charter) that an approved charter school authorizer authorized the charter school to operate in the state under the state''s charter school legislation. [CEDS Element: Charter School Contract Approval Date, ID:001652]';

