COMMENT ON COLUMN dbo.learning_standard_document.rights IS 'The information about rights held in and over the resource. [CEDS Element: Learning Standard Document Rights, ID:000885]';

COMMENT ON COLUMN dbo.learning_standard_document.rights_holder IS 'The person or organization owning or managing rights over the learning standards document. [CEDS Element: Learning Standard Document Rights Holder, ID:000886]';

COMMENT ON COLUMN dbo.learning_standard_document.learning_standard_document_publication_date IS 'The date on which this content was first published. [CEDS Element: Learning Standard Document Publication Date, ID:001569]';

