COMMENT ON COLUMN dbo.organization_federal_accountability.alternate_ayp_approach_indicator IS 'An indication of whether the district or school used an approved alternate approach for calculating Adequate Yearly Progress (AYP). [CEDS Element: Alternate Adequate Yearly Progress Approach Indicator, ID:000014]';

COMMENT ON COLUMN dbo.organization_federal_accountability.ayp_appeal_changed_designation IS 'An indication that the appeal resulted in a change in a school or district''s AYP designation. [CEDS Element: Adequate Yearly Progress Appeal Changed Designation, ID:000443]';

