COMMENT ON COLUMN dbo.program_participation_ae.ref_ae_functioning_level_at_posttest_id IS 'An individual''s skill level, as defined by the National Reporting System for Adult Education and determined by an approved standardized assessment after a set time period or number of instructional hours. [CEDS Element: Adult Educational Functioning Level at Posttest, ID:000780]';

