COMMENT ON COLUMN dbo.ps_student_enrollment.oral_defense_completed_indicator IS 'An indication of the individual''s completion of an oral defense. The requirement to conduct an oral defense by doctoral individuals may vary across institutions, programs, or fields of study. [CEDS Element: Oral Defense Completed Indicator, ID: 001416]';

