COMMENT ON COLUMN dbo.ps_student_enrollment.postsecondary_entering_student_ind IS 'The initial enrollment of an individual in credit bearing courses or developmental/remedial courses at an institution after completing high school or a high school equivalency program (e.g. GED, Adult High School Diploma). [CEDS Element: Postsecondary Entering Student Indicator, ID: 001426]';

